HELP NEW_XT_NEW_WIDGET                                  Steve Knight, Oct 93
                                                        SIREN Project

    new_xt_new_widget( WIDGETCLASS ) -> WIDGET_ALLOCATOR

This procedure takes a widgetclass and returns a widget constructor.
The constructor uses *XT_NEW_ARGS to perform argument processing for
the constructor.  It builds the widget using -XtVaCreateManagedWidget-.
